name: kakashi
dialogues: Naruto

name: kakashi
dialogues: Madara has seized control of the time dimension...

name: kakashi
dialogues: This multiverse we’re going to... It’s unstable

name: kakashi
dialogues: Chaotic...

name: kakashi
dialogues: Countless lives from different worlds are at stake.

name: kakashi
dialogues: Everyone is confused, scattered, and lost.

name: kakashi
dialogues: You’re the only one with the power to challenge him ...

name: kakashi
dialogues: But even you can’t do it alone.

name: kakashi
dialogues: Seek allies from other worlds. Some will help you

name: kakashi
dialogues: But others... May not even understand your words.

name: kakashi
dialogues: Answer their questions. Earn their trust...

name: kakashi
dialogues: And gain the strength you’ll need to face Madara.

name: kakashi
dialogues: The path ahead won’t be easy. But you must act quickly.

name: kakashi
dialogues: Time is slipping away. The multiverse is nearing collapse.

name: kakashi
dialogues: I’ll hold him off as long as I can. But you need to hurry!

name: kakashi
dialogues: Remember, the fate of all worlds now rests in your ...

name: kakashi
dialogues: Wait. What's happe...

name: eren
dialogues: This forest? It’s like being stuck in one of my titan fights.

name: eren
dialogues: Only this time. I’m the one running. No walls. No answers.

name: eren
dialogues: Madara bent space and time. He’s laughing at us.

name: eren
dialogues: Find your way Naruto. Prove you’re better than this maze.

name: eren
dialogues: I found this strange stone tablet on the ground. And trivia_1 carved right next to it.

name: rengoku
dialogues: A fire burns even in chaos. But this place is something else.

name: rengoku
dialogues: I’ve faced demons before. But this is beyond imagination.

name: rengoku
dialogues: Madara twisted the rules of time. Everyone is out of place.

name: rengoku
dialogues: If you focus your flame. You might just find a way through.

name: rengoku
dialogues: I found this strange stone tablet on the ground. And trivia_5 carved right next to it.

name: guts
dialogues: I've fought monsters and men. But this is pure madness.

name: guts
dialogues: Madara’s tricks make even the Eclipse seem straightforward.

name: guts
dialogues: Time's all twisted up here. He’s got us like puppets on strings.

name: guts
dialogues: Naruto. If you want to win. Don’t lose sight of who you are.

name: guts
dialogues: I found this strange stone tablet on the ground. And trivia_0 carved right next to it.

name: roshi
dialogues: Oh
column3: Naruto! Didn’t think I’d see you in this mess.

name: roshi
dialogues: Madara's turned time into his little playground of chaos.

name: roshi
dialogues: Back in my day. We only had evil emperors. Simple times.

name: roshi
dialogues: If you’re going to fix this. You’ll need more than strength!

name: roshi
dialogues: I found this strange stone tablet on the ground. And trivia_4 carved right next to it.

name: robin
dialogues: The markings here remind me of the Poneglyphs in my world.

name: robin
dialogues: Madara’s tampered with time itself. That’s no small feat.

name: robin
dialogues: It’s like he’s rewritten the rules of reality. Piece by piece.

name: robin
dialogues: Naruto. History holds answers. The past may guide you.

name: robin
dialogues: I found this strange stone tablet on the ground. And trivia_2 carved right next to it.

name: luffy
dialogues: Yo
column3: Naruto! This place is crazier than the Grand Line!

name: luffy
dialogues: Madara messed with time? Sounds like he’s asking for trouble.

name: luffy
dialogues: I bet he thinks he’s the King of Chaos or something. Hah!

name: luffy
dialogues: Let’s get him! But first. Show me you’ve got the guts for this.

name: luffy
dialogues: I found this strange stone tablet on the ground. And trivia_3 carved right next to it.

name: patrick
dialogues: HEY! Careful. This path in front of you is not for everyone!

name: patrick
dialogues: Darkness awaits within your mind.

name: patrick
dialogues: Many have already lost themselves along that path.

name: patrick
dialogues: Good luck!

name: gojo
dialogues: YOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!

name: gojo
dialogues: Took you long enough!

name: gojo
dialogues: Were u yapping in there?

name: gojo
dialogues: was it peter's fault????

name: gojo
dialogues: ANYWAYS!

name: gojo
dialogues: Let's meet on the north side of this place to kick Madara's ass!
